1. Navigated to the alx-intermediate-frontend repo.
2. Created a new directory called 0x03-sass_scss.
3. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm) with curl.
4. Closed and reopened the terminal.
5. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using nvm.
6. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 with the command: npm install sass -v 3.7.4
